RACE.RACE_TEXT: RUIDOSO DOWNS RACE 3 5F Dirt CR: 55. Trial Purse 8000. FOR REGISTERED NEW MEXICO BRED TWO YEAR OLDS THAT WERE NOMINATED AND REMAIN ELIGIBLE FOR THE 2023 MOUNTAIN TOP TB FUTURITY TRIALS. Weight 120 lbs. All horses must enter for trials on Friday June 2, 2023 by 11:00 AM and pay the $800 entry fee, if they ar e to run in the trials. Late nominations of $10,000 (includes all fees) will be accepted at time of entry into the trials.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: CHIPZ pressed the pace, challenged for the lead leaving the turn, dueled through the stretch and proved best in a long drive. TAX FREE TEXAS was unhurried early, dropped inside, rallied on the turn, angled out, swung wide, closed willingly and was gaining late. HORNS N HALOS set a pressured pace, drew clear briefly on the turn, dueled through the stretch, was in tight near the wire and was outfinished in a game effort. JUST KEEP LAUGHIN pressed the pace, bid inside to contend, was in tight late and outfinished in a good effort. MAKE UP A STORY broke awkwardly and was steadied at the start, raced in the back, advanced around the turn, bid three wide and finished well. HOLY BULLET stalked the pace towards the outside, rallied four wide on the turn, fell back into the stretch and hung late. SWEET BUT FIERCE showed speed to the turn, fell back and faded through the stretch. SI PASA ALGO raced close to the pace along the rail, was checked hard entering the turn and stopped.

ENTRY.OWNER: Robison J Kirk and Robison Judy
